  <heading>FDUP</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Broadcast floating-point immediate to vector elements (unpredicated)</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction unconditionally broadcasts the floating-point immediate into each element of the
destination vector. This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
  </desc>
